snippet.title: A Fox Tale - Official Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's the official Kickstarter trailer for my indie game A Fox Tale!


Check out the campaign here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/afoxtale/a-fox-tale


Here’s some social media links if you want to keep up to date with A Fox Tale:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AFoxTaleGame
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/afoxtalegame/
Discord: https://discord.gg/JUAHFQu
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AFoxTaleGame
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzYm7l7-PfwUiI5MZvIrctQ

Cheers guys!
Danny
